title: After All | snowboarding 08-09 Silent Progression Prd (Greece)
description:
After All is our latest project, a snowboard video filmed during the 2008 season.
The video is filmed in full HD format with the FX1 Sony Camcorder and it was released at the 29th of December 2008.
    It is filmed in Parnitha, Athens, Parnassos, Vasilitsa, Kaimaktsalan, Kalavrita, and Livigno during the winter season (Jan-April 08) and Les 2 Alpes Glacier during the summer season (June-July 08). The riders feauturing are Christian Manousaridis, Mike Avgeris, Konstantinos Vasiliadis, Alex Pitoulis, Dimitris Mavrokefalos, Adonis David, George Ouzounis, Dimitris Maniatis, Giannis Gripeos, CB, Christos Koutros, Giorgos Pikoulas, Kostis Migos and friends..
